What?!

232
00:20:31,661 --> 00:20:34,029
Can I tell you the truth?

233
00:20:34,764 --> 00:20:37,132
Truthfully... what?

234
00:20:40,536 --> 00:20:42,150
What is it?

235
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,641
Hey. You can say it from right there.

236
00:20:45,641 --> 00:20:47,310
