260
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:50,590
♫ For you, I love you only you ♫

261
00:22:50,590 --> 00:22:55,710
♫ Filled with excitement ♫

262
00:22:56,600 --> 00:23:02,180
♫ Softer than a coffee with good fragrance ♫

263
00:23:02,180 --> 00:23:04,690
